[30;1m539 | [0m[35m  `KeyVaultRSAPrivateKey` and `KeyVaultRSAPublicKey` classes that can use keys managed by Key Vault[0m

[30;1m541 | [0m[35m  `KeyVaultRSAPrivateKey` and `KeyVaultRSAPublicKey`, respectively[0m

[30;1m572 | [0m[35m## 4.8.0b2 (2022-11-15)[0m
[30;1m573 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m574 | [0m[35m### Features Added[0m
[30;1m575 | [0m[35m- Added support for service API version `7.4-preview.1`[0m
[30;1m576 | [0m[35m- `KeyClient` has a `create_okp_key` method to create an octet key pair (OKP) on Managed HSM[0m
[30;1m577 | [0m[35m- Added `eddsa` to `SignatureAlgorithm` enum to support signing and verifying using an[0m
[30;1m578 | [0m[35m  Edwards-Curve Digital Signature Algorithm (EdDSA) on Managed HSM[0m
